        {
            "id": 6430158,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 櫃買市場加權指數下跌-20.42點至374.66點，跌幅5.17%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間23日11:33，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌20.42點（或5.17%），暫報374.66點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+9.79%</li><li>近 1 月：+20.3%</li><li>近 3 月：+32.66%</li><li>近 6 月：+49.39%</li><li>今年以來：+43.02%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>SDN概念領跌-8.51%。其中    安瑞-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3664:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3664\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3664-TW</a>)            下跌        9.89%            ;        華星光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>)            下跌        9.38%            ;        明泰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3380:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3380\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3380-TW</a>)            下跌        9.13%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>車用記憶體概念領跌-7.44%。其中    詮欣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6205:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6205\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6205-TW</a>)            下跌        9.98%            ;        力旺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3529:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3529\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3529-TW</a>)            下跌        9.25%            ;        福懋科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8131-TW</a>)            下跌        8.44%    。</p></section></main>",
